title.narrative: Stabilisation Unit component for Humanitarian and Emergency Support service

description.narrative: This activity (Stabilisation Unit component for Humanitarian and Emergency Support service) is a component of DFID Humanitarian and Emergency Operations Support Service reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £11,889,995. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Material relief assistance and services . , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-05-2012 and the end date is 31-10-2017.
